api_list.name: Get Horoscope (Multilingual)
api_list.description: Return horoscope information by sign, period, type and languages provided.

required_parameters.name: language
required_parameters.description:
en: English, 
zh-t: Chinese (transditional), 
zh-s: Chinese (simplified),
es: Spanish,
hi: Hindu,
fr: French,
ja: Japanese,
ko: Korean

required_parameters.name: type
required_parameters.description: Depend on period, use **Get Types** method to get available types for the selected period.

api_list.name: Get Signs
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://horoscopes-ai.p.rapidapi.com/get_signs"

headers = {
            "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
            "X-RapidAPI-Host": "horoscopes-ai.p.rapidapi.com"
        }

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)
print(response.json())
